US farmers markets

Source: R/farmers_markets.r
farmers_markets.Rd

Dataset of all farmers markets in the US

farmers_markets

Format

A data frame with 8788 rows and 9 variables:

FMID

integer Unique Farmers Market ID

MarketName

character Name of Farmers Market

street

character Street

city

character City

County

character County

State

integer State

zip

character zip code

x

double longitude

y

double latitude

Source

https://apps.ams.usda.gov/FarmersMarketsExport/ExcelExport.aspx

Details

Dataset which includes the location and ID for every Farmers Market in the US
